-------1) It would interesting to see a way to play as the Corruptrons either in singleplayer or multiplayer.-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------2) A way to save creations would save a lot of time as well as giving the players a way to hurry past the parts of the game  he/she may find tedious.-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------3) In Sandbox mode it is super fun to just go nuts and build a bunch of stuff but it would be interesting to see how such creations would fair in Invasion Mode, but it can be boring to have to rebuild them block by block (especially if they are large creations). So a way to put Corruptrons in Sandbox Mode would be fun and allow players to test their creations before starting an Invasion Mode playthrough.-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------4) It would be fun to be able to rename the Bricktrons to names that are more personal or funny.-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Thats my thoughts on Castle Story. I look forward to seeing how the game developes.I hope this review has been helpful. Thank You for reading it.-Mr.DuckP.S.: I love the Castle Story website."
